OL,3,CYoung Oldham filmmaker produces short
OL,4,Cfilm starring a Coronation Street actor
OL,6,FA young filmmaker from Oldham has
OL,7,Fproduced his very first short film
OL,8,Fstarring a Coronation Street actor.
OL,10,FSaleem Miah's film 'Spice for life' is
OL,11,Fbased it on his own experience of
OL,12,Fgrowing up in the foster care system.
OL,14,FHis film, which is shot entirely in
OL,15,Fthe North West, stars Coronation
OL,16,Fstreet actor Adam Hussain and
OL,17,FHollyoaks actress Kirsty-Leigh Porter.
OL,19,FThe film is about a care worker who
OL,20,Ffails to bond with her foster son
OL,21,Funtil they connect over cooking.
