OL,3,CYoung Oldham filmmaker produces short
OL,4,Cfilm starring a Coronation Street actor
OL,6,FSaleem wrote, produced and directed
OL,7,Fthe film which is being screened as
OL,8,Fpart of Manchester Metropolitan
OL,9,FUniversity's 2025 Filmmaking cohort.
OL,11,FSaleem said: "I grew up in foster care
OL,12,Fmyself, I moved about quite a lot. I
OL,13,Fgrew up in Oldham, and I was placed
OL,14,Fwith a lot of white families, which I
OL,15,Fthink is quite like a unique,
OL,16,Finteresting. upbringing.
OL,18,F"I've always wanted to make a film
OL,19,Fabout it. The story it's fictional,
OL,20,Fbut a lot of the scenes in it I have
OL,21,Fkind of got from my own life, really.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
