OL,6,F"But I've been really lucky in the
OL,7,Fsense that I've met people along the
OL,8,Fway that have supported me."
OL,10,FHe added: "I feel like people have
OL,11,Fassumptions, don't they, and they sort
OL,12,Fof assume that kids and care face,
OL,13,Fyou're not very smart or, like, you're
OL,14,Fa troublemaker, you're not ambitious.
OL,16,F"I've always wanted to be an example
OL,17,Fof someone that doesn't sort of fit
OL,18,Fthose stereotypes and it just proving
OL,19,Fthat we can be just as good as anyone
OL,20,Felse at something and we can live
OL,21,Fthrough it like really good lives."
