OL,3,CYoung Oldham filmmaker produces short
OL,4,Cfilm starring a Coronation Street actor
OL,6,FSaleem is a third year Filmmaking
OL,7,Fstudent from Manchester and is also a
OL,8,Frecipient of the RTS Beryl Vertue
OL,9,FScholarship, supported by Hartswood
OL,10,FFilms bosses Sue and Debbie Vertue,
OL,11,Fwho mentor him.
OL,13,FHe began his journey into the industry
OL,14,Fthrough a local BFI talent development
OL,15,Fscheme, going on to gain a place on
OL,16,Fthe NFTS Film Academy.
OL,18,FThe young filmaker is keen to dedicate
OL,19,Fhis career to getting underrepresented
OL,20,Fvoices on screen.
